      "solution": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Accessible Navigation</title>\n    <style>\n        .skip-link {\n            position: absolute;\n            left: -9999px;\n            top: 0;\n            background: #000;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 10px;\n            z-index: 100;\n        }\n        .skip-link:focus {\n            left: 0;\n        }\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <a href=\"#main-content\" class=\"skip-link\">Skip to main content</a>\n    \n    <header>\n        <h1>WebLearn Academy</h1>\n        <nav aria-label=\"Main\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"/\">Home</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/courses\">Courses</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/about\">About</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n    \n    <nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\">\n        <ol>\n            <li><a href=\"/\">Home</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"/courses\">Courses</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"/courses/html\" aria-current=\"page\">HTML Fundamentals</a></li>\n        </ol>\n    </nav>\n    \n    <main id=\"main-content\">\n        <h2>HTML Fundamentals Course</h2>\n        <p>Course content goes here...</p>\n    </main>\n    \n    <footer>\n        <nav aria-label=\"Footer\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/terms\">Terms of Service</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/sitemap\">Sitemap</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n        <p>&copy; 2026 WebLearn Academy</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"
